      "question": "Evaluate $\\frac{\\tan 65^\\circ}{\\cot 25^\\circ}$.",
      "answer": "1",
      "solution": {
        "steps": [
          "Use the complementary angle identity $\\cot \\theta = \\tan(90^\\circ - \\theta)$.",
          "Substitute $\\cot 25^\\circ = \\tan(90^\\circ - 25^\\circ) = \\tan 65^\\circ$ and simplify."
        ],
        "derivation": "\\frac{\\tan 65^\\circ}{\\tan(90^\\circ - 25^\\circ)} = \\frac{\\tan 65^\\circ}{\\tan 65^\\circ} = 1"
      },
